### Health Check
# @name Health Check
GET http://{{host}}/api/health

### Collectors - Syndication Feed

# @name Run Collectors_Feed Load All Posts
POST http://{{host}}/api/CollectorsFeedLoadAllPosts?userOid={{entraOid}}&CheckFrom=2026-01-01

###
# @name Run Collectors_Feed Load All Posts - No Date
POST http://{{host}}/api/CollectorsFeedLoadAllPosts?userOid={{entraOid}}

###
# @name Run Collectors_SpeakingEngagements Load All Engagements
POST http://{{host}}/api/CollectorsSpeakingEngagementsLoadAll?userOid={{entraOid}}&CheckFrom=2026-02-02

###
# @name Run Collectors_SpeakingEngagements Load All Engagements - No Date
POST http://{{host}}/api/CollectorsSpeakingEngagementsLoadAll?userOid={{entraOid}}

###
# @name Run Collectors_YouTube Load All Videos
POST http://{{host}}/api/CollectorsYouTubeLoadAllVideos?userOid={{entraOid}}&CheckFrom=2025-06-12

###
# @name Run Collectors_YouTube Load All Videos - No Date
POST http://{{host}}/api/CollectorsYouTubeLoadAllVideos?userOid={{entraOid}}

###
# @name Refresh Facebook Token
POST https://jjgnet-broadcast.azurewebsites.net/admin/functions/FacebookTokenRefresh

x-functions-key: {{functions-key}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}
